Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 9/27/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about some of the biggest topics in hip hop and entertainment. Today, it's Friday vibes! They have a big debate on bikers vs drivers on the road, discuss the Jeffrey Dahmer series, as well as your favorites such as Ride Or Die, Curved, and the Guru!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
